if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n15年前中學畢業sor"},{"pid":"73496242ffa9fb5fd4ad29f7969223817ec2f179","tid":454890,"uid":49707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:16:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基本常識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中幾開始學imaginary number呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\npure不嬲都教"},{"pid":"989f18a7d5d66ab88c85102f68b70aa17a92bf87","tid":454890,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T01:35:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>X^2 &gt;0        X二次方大於0   呢個係基本常識？<br />\n------------------------------------------------<br />\nX=5j            j係complex number =開方-1<br />\nj^2=-1<br />\nX^2 = 5^2 乘  j^2 =-25<br />\n-25&gt;0 ?</blockquote><br />\n0^2 = 0。<br />\n<br />\n即係唔係 &gt;<br />\n<br />\n利申文科人行過"},{"pid":"b0a0f22a2487d9e1808d735910afbdda27bcdd4f","tid":454890,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T01:36:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>X^2 &gt;0        X二次方大於0   呢個係基本常識？<br />\n------------------------------------------------<br />\nX=5j            j係complex number =開方-1<br />\nj^2=-1<br />\nX^2 = 5^2 乘  j^2 =-25<br />\n-25&gt;0 ?</blockquote><br />\n0^2 = 0。<br />\n<br />\n即係唔係 &gt;<br />\n<br />\n利申文科人行過</blockquote><br />\n自膠睇漏咗你之後個補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3c9e8040593eafddc87422b90faac252b1b257","tid":454890,"uid":8550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T01:42:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">x^2&gt;0 &forall;x&isin; <strong>R</strong>\\{0}</span>"},{"pid":"7e8352c96b10de7da727bb6a42b55d6dd9718d6b","tid":454890,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T01:45:45.000Z","msg":"首先 j或者叫i係虛數(imaginary number)<br />\n無法定義<br />\n你唔可以話 3i 大過 0 或者 4-9i 細過 2<br />\n你係無法作出比較<br />\n<br />\n如果你自乘<br />\ni^2 = -1<br />\n當乘的時候變成乘-1<br />\ninequality符號要轉<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n-3 &lt; 4<br />\n兩邊 除負1或者乘負1<br />\n3 &gt; -4<br />\n符號要轉方向"},{"pid":"d9bf8d5057f39cd792b95cea6ce3831c9c6e0a68","tid":454890,"uid":50428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T01:55:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先 j或者叫i係虛數(imaginary number)<br />\n無法定義<br />\n你唔可以話 3i 大過 0 或者 4-9i 細過 2<br />\n你係無法作出比較<br />\n<br />\n如果你自乘<br />\ni^2 = -1<br />\n當乘的時候變成乘-1<br />\ninequality符號要轉<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n-3 &lt; 4<br />\n兩邊 除負1或者乘負1<br />\n3 &gt; -4<br />\n符號要轉方向</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.  3i 大唔大過0我就唔知, imaginary 同real應該比較唔到 <br />\n2.  4-9i 就一定大過2  real part 4&gt;2<br />\n3. 佢乘ROOT -1,  唔洗轉。 <br />\n=&gt; 因為 X^2&gt; 0 係real number (唔包0) 先岩"}]}